 Abuja, FCT  This is contained in a statement signed by the Special Assistant (Media) to FCT Minister, Abubakar Sani, yesterday in Abuja. Accordingly, the Chief of Staff to the FCT Minister, Muhammad Bornu, is to oversee the activities of the transport secretariat while the general manager of FCT Hospital Services Management Board, Dr. Aminu Mai, takes charge of the health and human services secretariat. Similarly, member of the Secondary Education Board, Sunny Monedafe, oversees the affairs of the board, while the director, FCT Muslim Pilgrims Welfare Board, Bashir Muhammad, isuperintends the social development secretariat. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .